[goal]
Decide whether main is ready to ship v1.4 normatively.

[context]
- All v0.7-v0.11 surface cleanup has merged
- Deadlines + typed-checks design docs are stable
- Backward compat preserved (v=1.1, v=1.2, v=1.3 still validate)

[constraints]
- Don't ship if pytest is red on main
- Don't ship without CHANGELOG verified
- Wire format remains additive (per SPEC §8)

[handoff]
- id=verify   to=any     do=run scripts/publish.sh --test on TestPyPI    deadline=2026-05-15
- id=tag      to=human   do=tag v1.0.0 and push                          deadline=2026-05-15T17:00:00Z   after=verify
- id=publish  to=human   do=run scripts/publish.sh                       deadline=2026-05-16T00:00:00Z   after=tag

[checks]
- pytest                 :: pass
- coverage               :: pass    value=87       threshold=85    op=>=    unit=%
- spec_amendment         :: pass    note=§§11.4, 21.1.1, 21.1.2 added
- hallucinated_tool_call :: pass
- circular_reference     :: pass
- token_budget_exceeded  :: pass    value=2400     threshold=8000  op=<=    unit=tokens
